                    <h1 class="domdom">27</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/359">People And Planet Season: We Feed The World (2005)</a></h1>

                    <h2>27 Feb 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>A film about food and globalisation, fishermen and farmers, long-distance lorry drivers and high-powered corporate executives, the flow of goods and cash flow–a film about scarcity amid plenty. With its unforgettable images, the film provides insight into the production of our food and answers the question what world hunger has to do with us.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/359">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
