                    <h1 class="domdom">11</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/361">People And Planet Season: Between Midnight And The Rooster&#39;s Crow (2005)</a></h1>

                    <h2>11 Mar 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>In the aggressive search for the 'black gold' that drives Western economies, multinational corporations are working to extract billions of dollars of oil reserves from beneath Ecuador's rainforest. This documentary investigates how the operations of the Canadian EnCana corporation are answerable for widespread environmental contamination and human rights violations in the region.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/361">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
